# üìù ENHANCED SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Get Groq API key from https://console.groq.com/ (REQUIRED for current info)
# 3. Get OpenWeatherMap API key from https://openweathermap.org/api (OPTIONAL - for weather)
# 4. Get NewsAPI key from https://newsapi.org (OPTIONAL - for news)
# 5. Replace placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 6. Make sure Groq key starts with gsk_ (underscore format)
# 7. Start Ollama: sudo systemctl start ollama  
# 8. Download model: ollama pull nemotron-mini:4b-instruct-q4_K_M
# 9. Run Pascal: python main.py

